Package: umc
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyside6.qtcore | python3-pyside6, python3-pyside6.qtgui | python3-pyside6, python3-pyside6.qtqml | python3-pyside6, python3-pyside6.qtquick | python3-pyside6, android-tools-adb, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: python3-pyside6.qtnetwork, python3-pyside6.qtwidgets, python3-pyside6.qtopengl
Description: Unified Mobile Controller
 A desktop application for managing Android devices and launching applications
 in isolated virtual displays using scrcpy and adb.
 .
 This application provides a graphical interface to interact with Android devices
 connected via USB or TCP/IP. It allows users to browse installed applications
 and launch them in separate, native-like windows on the desktop.